<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card bg-darker col-md">
			<!--<img class="card-img-top hidden-md-down" src="../assets/images/AcFav.png" alt="Card image cap">-->
            <h5 class="card-header bg-darker text-center">Featured</h5> 
			<div class="card-block">
		    	<h4 class="card-title">Animal Crossing</h4>
				<p class="card-text">Creative application that brings the daily soundtracks of Animal Crossing back, and now it's here to stay for our daily endeavors unlike never before. Able to choose smoothly between the user's desired Generation, from the hit classics like, original Animal Crossing from GameCube, to City Folk from the WII U, and the latest New Leaf on the 3DS. Built with the MEEN stack, backend API through Mongodb.</p>
                
                <div class="pos-f-t">
                    <div class="collapse" id="AC_App-Info">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <div class="list-group">

                                <div class="list-group-item"><strong>MEEN Stack</strong>:
                                    <span class="badge badge-default badge-pill px-2 py-2">Mongo</span>
                                    <span class="badge badge-default badge-pill px-2 py-2">Express</span>
                                    <span class="badge badge-default badge-pill px-2 py-2">Ember</span>
                                    <span class="badge badge-default badge-pill px-2 py-2">Node.js</span>
                                </div>
                                <div  class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>SASS</strong> : Modulated CSS</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>jQuery</strong> : used with API controls</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>ES2015</strong> : latest JavaScript practices</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-darker">
                        <button class="btn-outline-info navbar-toggler " type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#AC_App-Info" aria-controls="navbarToggleExternalContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                            <span>Essentials &omega;</span>
                        </button>
                    </nav>
                </div>

                <!-- Modal controller-->
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary float-right" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#ac-tunes">
                    <img class="d-none d-md-inline" width="150" src="../assets/images/AcFav.png">
                    <span>Launch App</span>
                </button>

                <!-- Modal -->
                <div class="modal fade bg-darker" id="ac-tunes" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="ac-tunes" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                            <div class="modal-header bg-darker text-white">
                                <h5 class="modal-title mx-auto" id="ac-tunes">Animal Crossing Tunes</h5>
                                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-white">&times;</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-body bg-darker text-white">
                                {{#ac-tunes}}{{/ac-tunes}}
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-footer bg-darker text-white">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div><!--/modal -->
			</div>
        </div>
	</div>
	
	 <div class="col-md-6">
		<div class="card bg-darker col-md">
			<!--<img class="card-img-top hidden-md-down" src="../assets/images/UndertaleFav.png" alt="Card image cap">-->
			<div class="card-block">
				<h4 class="card-title">Undertale</h4>
				<p class="card-text">Recreational Project that restructures the original Site to a more update formality. Built using Ember, my first project I've built as a Developer. Complete overhaul of hands-on coding and features that utilize API information for the user's discretion. Allows fans to post "Mail" on the site for the Undertale Devs to see, and others to respond to. Built with Ember.js, Backend localStorage.</p>

                <div class="pos-f-t">
                    <div class="collapse" id="UT_App-info">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <div class="list-group">
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>Ember</strong>: JavaScript Framework</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>localStorage</strong> : Ember data for 'Fan Mail' feature, (stand alone version only)</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>SASS</strong> : Modulated CSS</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>jQuery</strong> : used with API controls</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="list-group-item">
                                    <span><strong>ES2015</strong> : latest JavaScript practices</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-darker">
                        <button class="btn-outline-info navbar-toggler " type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#UT_App-info" aria-controls="navbarToggleExternalContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                            <span>Essentials &omega;</span>
                        </button>
                    </nav>
                </div>

				{{#link-to 'undertale' class="btn btn-primary float-right"}}
				    <img class="d-none d-md-inline" width="150" src="../assets/images/UndertaleFav.png">
				    <span>Preview</span>
				{{/link-to}}
			</div>
	    </div>
	 </div>


  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="card bg-darker col-md">
      <div class="card-block">
        <h4 class="card-title">Sinmod Vote Roulette</h4>
        <p class="card-text">Testing 7 days to die Server API for data mining.</p>

        <!-- Modal controller-->
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary float-right" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#sinmod">
          <span>Preview data</span>
        </button>

        <!-- Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade bg-darker" id="sinmod" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="ac-tunes" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
              <div class="modal-header bg-darker text-white">
                <h5 class="modal-title mx-auto" id="sinmod">Sinmod Datamine</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                  <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-white">&times;</span>
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="modal-body bg-darker text-white">
                {{render "sinmod"}}
              </div>
              <div class="modal-footer bg-darker text-white">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--/modal -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>